The paper deals with image captioning using natural language questions, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the need for continuous learning and expanding knowledge, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach using the MSCOCO dataset, which is commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
